# Why Base App + Farcaster Are Key for Base Chain Global Expansion

Base (Coinbase L2) + Farcaster (decentralized social) = the perfect combo for worldwide onchain adoption.

Base App brings easy wallet/social features; Farcaster adds permissionless, open social graph. Together: Global reach beyond borders.

## Why This Matters
- Base App: Seamless onboarding, Basenames, feeds/chat.
- Farcaster: Own your data, Frames for mini-apps, true web3 social.
- Global Expansion: Low fees + decentralized = access for emerging markets.

## Stats & Vision
- Base TVL exploding (2025 surge).
- Farcaster users growing fast.
- Coinbase pushing both for "global financial freedom".

